719879f-a.folder: Frankfort Street & Gold Street, Manhattan, NY
719879f-a.text:
Frankfort Street, south side, west from and including Gold Street.

723074f-a.folder: Rose Street & Frankfort Street, Manhattan, NY
723074f-a.text:
Rose Street, west side, north from Frankfort, to the Brooklyn Bridge, (shown on the right). Also shown is Frankfort Street, north side, west from Rose Street.

P. L. Sperr.
